high_descs: Go forward to the tub.  Turn right and face the tub.
Pick up the wash rag on the left.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the wash rag in the sink.  Turn the water on to get it wet.  Turn the water off.
Turn around and go to the dresser.
Put the wash rag on the dresser to the left of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Get a wash rag wet to put on the dresser.

high_descs: Walk straight towards the bath tub.
